modName: Nude and bunny Dragonscale armor CBBE
summary: Dragonscale armor re-mod, containing nude version and bunny-suit like version.
descriptionHtml:
This is made with nifskope and dxtbmp only.
So if there is any problem of 3D problem, like the skin is outside of armor, I maybe can\'t fix that.

NOTE: only support non-slim CBBE version now

Although nude version is too nasty, but I think the bunny version wasn\'t made very well.

=nude= almost nude dragonscale armor mod
=bunny= just made for non-nude, but it\'s so strange to just add underwear, so I tried to made like a bunny-suit

If there is any problem, plz feel free to report in comment. 
Although I\'m a little busy recently, I will response or fix the problems when I have time.
author: uraleya
